# Keep input files if they are part of the repo structure, but exclude data generated during runs
# The .gitignore lists *.csv, *.pdb, etc. but setup.py includes package data.
# We should be careful. 
# Dockerignore should generally exclude temporary/output data.
# We'll allow source files but exclude bulky outputs if any are in the root source tree.
